cast.overview: Women enter and exit a science fiction author's life over the course of a few years after the author loses the woman he considers his one true love.

details.biography:
Alice Lee was born in Hong Kong but grew up in Sydney where she studied at the Actor's Centre. She then moved to London to continue her training and this is where she currently resides. She has been in many film, commercial and television productions throughout her career. She has trained with  Actor’s Centre (Sydney, 00-01),

Actor’s Centre (London,continuous)

Method Acting with Sam Rumbelow (2009-2010),

Margie Haber Studio (L.A., 2010),

Voice with Anne Walsh (2010-11).
